preSteps()

preSteps perform the previous steps before propagating annotations. These steps include: 1) filter data, 2) resolve conflicts, 3) resolve agreements, 4) remove duplicates, 5) convert frequency to scores, 6) remove duplicate lines, 7) ensure Taxid and Parent_tax_id are are character vectors.
